{"tid":784554,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"神鬼、靈魂、外星人的證明","createTime":"2018-08-18T13:03:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T13:22:04.000Z","uid":149978,"like":3,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"b2a3bb59688857feda3bfe214a1278fb4dd6679b","tid":784554,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T13:03:48.000Z","msg":"其實前世回溯、瀕死經驗、通靈、宗教經驗、神蹟經驗，自古到今，在全球都有報告。<br />\n<br />\n有部分係假，有部分係大腦作崇/發夢當真。<br />\n<br />\n但只要有一個個案係堅，就已經證實有鬼神和靈魂。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有大量疑似鬼魂的cctv報告<br />\n<br />\n雖然好多係流（改圖/物理現象）<br />\n但只要一個係真，就證明有鬼神存在。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n外星人在世界各地都有報告。<br />\n雖然好多都證實左係流（假野/改圖/物理現象/大腦作崇）<br />\n但只要有其中一個報告係真，就證明有外星人在地球有活動。"},{"pid":"b3acc46bb6db5898c0ef9707dabf28095c2332d1","tid":784554,"uid":31511,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T13:06:13.000Z","msg":"所以呢"},{"pid":"beea015f022e77f3570d5cf848f1449945dbb2c1","tid":784554,"uid":198822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T13:07:03.000Z","msg":"咁真個啲證據係邊?<br />\n冇仲講條撚咩"},{"pid":"bc8f4f2e8ef8311c008662939474a2b19dfb404d","tid":784554,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"b3acc46bb6db5898c0ef9707dabf28095c2332d1","tid":784554,"uid":31511,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T13:06:13.000Z","msg":"所以呢"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T13:07:22.000Z","msg":"有鬼神/靈魂/外星人在地球活動<br />\n機會並不低"},{"pid":"b1377d33c916c14bb99839fdc3280436e7e2231b","tid":784554,"uid":31511,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bc8f4f2e8ef8311c008662939474a2b19dfb404d","tid":784554,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"b3acc46bb6db5898c0ef9707dabf28095c2332d1","tid":784554,"uid":31511,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T13:06:13.000Z","msg":"所以呢"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T13:07:22.000Z","msg":"有鬼神/靈魂/外星人在地球活動<br />\n機會並不低"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T13:08:10.000Z","msg":"你係點樣推論出不低<img src=\"/assets/faces